1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,780
WindWalker is a GPT-powered web app builder for small businesses.

2
00:00:07,740 --> 00:00:11,840
A user describes the business they want to run.

3
00:00:12,660 --> 00:00:22,820
For example, a digital bookstore with member login, cart, checkout,
purchase history, downloads, and an operator dashboard.

4
00:00:22,820 --> 00:00:37,980
WindWalker turns that request into a workflow pattern, generates a responsive
web app preview, and lets the user refine it through conversation.

5
00:00:39,180 --> 00:00:45,440
When the app is ready, it is deployed to Cloudflare Pages as a live URL.

6
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:55,840
In this demo, the deployed bookstore supports mock member login,
product browsing, cart interaction, and test checkout.

7
00:00:56,620 --> 00:01:06,740
The same workflow can be adapted for bookings, quotes, customer intake,
support, and other small-business operations.

8
00:01:07,740 --> 00:01:23,040
We used GPT-5.6 for final iteration and validation, with OpenAI Codex
supporting implementation, testing, and submission evidence.

9
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:26,120
GPT can generate an app.

10
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:39,680
WindWalker helps small-business owners launch, operate, fix, and continuously
improve that app with workflow patterns and lightweight human support.
